arts.ttl: Espanyol star to miss Real Sociedad clash through suspension
arts.sum: Espanyol will be forced to see out the club’s upcoming meeting with Real Sociedad without the contributions of a key performer. The player in question? Carlos Romero. Versatile left-back Romero…
